GENERAL NOTES

ccROJ - Time-Frequency C++ Framework is an opensource project published under GNU GPL license. Please see LICENSE file. You can check version number of this software in VERSION file. This framework is dedicated to Linux platforms. It has been tested on GNU Linux OS (GNU Debian, version: stretch/sid). The main purpose of this project is presented in MANIFEST file.

NOTES ABOUT AUTHORS

Please check authorship and contact to the authors in AUTHORS file.

