D. Fourer, F. Auger, K. Czarnecki, S. Meignen, P. Flandrin, "Chirp rate and instantaneous frequency estimation: application to recursive vertical synchrosqueezing", IEEE Signal Processing Letters, 2017.

NOTES ABOUT BUILDING, TESTING & INSTALL

Please compile the project by: make (see also DEPENDENCIES file)
Please install the project by: make install (see INSTALL file)
The manual will be generated by: make doc
The resultant documentation will be placed in "manual" sub-directory
You can packed the project into a zip archive by: make zip
Please use makefile in "testing" sub-directory to run user cases.

NOTES FOR DEVELOPERS 

Please use the prefix a_ for variables given as function arguments.
Please use the prefix m_ for variables which are members of objects.
Please use the prefix roj_ for any definition of new data structures.
Please use the suffix _config for any definition of config structures.
Please use the prefix roj_ also for any definition of new objects.

